.SH DESCRIPTION
The \fBcmf\fR file type template provides simple hilighting and indentation of
Adobe Macromedia ColdFusion pages embedded within 
.Ht html 9 
files. The keywords from \fBColdFusion MX 7\fR are supported.
.PP
The template supports  highlighting and indention of the tags \fC<cfxxx>\fR in
addition to \fC<cfscript>\fR blocks and \fC<cfquery>\fR SQL blocks.
